bug.short_desc: Konsole title doesn't update to current program or host run.
bug.cf_doc_type: If docs needed, set a value

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 1205265 SSH to host not matching tab/title displayed.
Description of problem:
The title/tab stays at whatever the first program run, not the current one. See attachments below. This is identical to:
https://bugs.kde.org/show_bug.cgi?id=368785
Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
konsole5-16.08.1-1.fc24.x86_64 konsole5-part-16.08.1-1.fc24.x86_64
How reproducible:
Every time. Even across reboots.
Steps to Reproduce: 1. Open Konsole 2. run command 3. tab/title changes to whatever the first command run with this version package installed.
Actual results: See #3 above.
Expected results: Tab/Title updates to whatever current command/host is being run.
Additional info:
upstream patches applied, updates submitted (this bug should get updated when they are pushed to -testing/-stable repos)
